{
  "texts": [
    "In particular, the multi-actor approach shows significance in all key-insights.",
    "However, the results of vector similarity differ from those of GPT-4, with no significant statistical differences observed across all key-insights for Mixtral FT and InternLM2 FT. Yi FT shows significance only in aim, methods, and findings.",
    "This may be due to the fact that vector similarity is less sensitive to semantic variations.",
    "Figure 1b illustrates this point by demonstrating that the variance of vector similarity between different models is lower, resulting in closer curves.",
    "Nevertheless, the multi-actor approach shows significance in all key-insights except aim."
  ]
